title: Ceiling fans included, Spacious 9' ceilings, Stylish private cabanas

posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Dog park and dog wash station for our 4-legged residents', '-Kitchen islands with designer pendant lighting in select floorplans', '-Designer lighting and plumbing fixtures', '-Ceiling fans included', '-11,000 SF of ground level retail with valet parking', '-Signature two and three bedroom townhome floor plans with 2-car garages and penthouse level residences available', '-Individually controlled heating and air conditioning with Nest thermostats', '-Washer and dryer in every residence', '-Community room, business center, Wi-Fi lounge', '-Summer kitchen pavilion including grills, pizza oven and refrigeration', '-Wood flooring throughout the kitchen, living and dining areas', '-Wi-Fi access throughout residential amenities', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
